<h1>Youngest director</h1>

<% directors_with_dob = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil})%>
<% descending_dob = directors_with_dob.all.order({:dob => :desc})%>
<% youngest_director = descending_dob.at(0)%>

<%youngest_director_dob = youngest_director.dob%>
<%formatted_date_string = youngest_director_dob.strftime("%B %d, %Y")%>

<p>The youngest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%=youngest_director.id%>"><%= youngest_director.name%></a>, born on <%=formatted_date_string%>.</p>

<p>(<a href="http://strftime.net/" target="_blank">http://strftime.net/</a> is handy for putting together the formatting strings for the <code>.strftime</code> method.)</p>
